    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i mean i know you have to say to talk to a doctor but i've read so much about how much garlic can actually thin the blood. if i just took really high doses of garlic extract and kept my greens high, wouldn't that basically do the same thing as the warfarin without all the side effects and the testing? like, can't i just use that to manage it myself?",
